   <body>
      <p>You must add the following values in the Business Objects picklist in the Deal
            Guidance Dimension Sets object, to use them to configure Deal Maximizer rules. </p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <i>Apttus_Config2__LineItem__c</i>
         </li>
         <li>
            <i>Apttus_Config2__ProductConfiguration__c</i>
         </li>
      </ul>
      <p>You must also define field dependencies, if they are not already created, on the
            <uicontrol>Guidance Type</uicontrol> field to complete the configuration of the Deal
            Guidance Dimension Sets object.</p>
